{"about_the_game":"Hey rookie, climb aboard! We're heading for adventure across the North Sea on our reliable Viking ship! Choose from one of the charismatic characters, hire some warriors and engage in bloody battles!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879050/extras/Header_open-world_eng.png?t=1724232941\" /><br>Your character travels around the large world based on Scandinavian mythology. <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>There are various settlements located on the map. <br></li><li>Pirate and merchant ships are traveling on the seas. <br></li><li>Caves and ruins of ancient civilizations hide treasures. </li></ul>Interact with the world! You can trade, employ recruits or simply plunder all and receive valuable resources by force!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879050/extras/Open_World.gif?t=1724232941\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879050/extras/Header_crew-management_eng.png?t=1724232941\" /><br>The player has to employ a team which helps him fight. <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>All units have their own specialization such as soldiers and others performing support functions on the ship - cooking, treatment, navigation, etc. <br></li><li>Each warrior reaches new levels by receiving points from successful battles.<br></li><li>Warriors need a salary, food and victorious battles to support their levels of morale! <br></li><li>Carefully watch over the crew members! They can be wounded, develop bad habits or catch diseases.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879050/extras/Crew_managment.gif?t=1724232941\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879050/extras/Header_battles_eng.png?t=1724232941\" /><br>At last, your brave team of cheerful, bearded bandits lands in the coastal village. The nose of the Viking ship sticks into the shore, and warriors led by your character jump out on the land! <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dynamic battles in a beat'em'up style with tactical elements. <br></li><li>You control the main hero and issue commands to your crew members.  <br></li><li>Your warriors have their own intelligence - they react appropriately to different situations on the battlefield.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879050/extras/Battles.gif?t=1724232941\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879050/extras/Header_rpg_eng.png?t=1724232941\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Improve the skills of your hero to get access to additional abilities and quests.<br></li><li>Use various types of weapons and armor. <br></li><li>Purchase different ships and equip them to your needs. <br></li><li>Complete the storyline and additional side-quests.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Commander","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/879050/21d83b30deefb09c7dd65a721acc83d77a606afd.jpg"},{"name":"First steps","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/879050/01a873ec7674acafcb9407eb2c6a17f263d10777.jpg"},{"name":"Beaten but not broken!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/879050/f43e368b8df8839cd05b0d04457b903ade57414e.jpg"},{"name":"Run, Tosti, run!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/879050/415a5cf1bb63c6f6ab70bf9dbdb7b90c3a791125.jpg"},{"name":"Tomb raider","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/879050/dbd8d3b1876e29b9d6e25b2c95564503fb4b0c47.jpg"},{"name":"Peacemaker","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/879050/64b3524c8fd53b5a